Zuta Mary Nartey (nke a na-akpọkwa Mary Zutah Narteh, amụrụ na 14 Nọvemba na afo 1987) bụ onye Ghana na-atụpu javelin.
N'afọ 2012, ọ nọ n'ọkwa nke anọ na African Championships in Athletics na Porto Novo na mita 49.69.

N'afọ 2014, ọ nọ n'ọnọdụ nke iri na otu na Commonwealth Games na Glasgow, merie ọlaọcha na African Championships in Athletics na Marrakech na mita 52.57, ọ bụkwa nke asatọ na IAAF Continental Cup na Marramech.
O nwetakwara ihe nrite ọlaọcha na Africa Games na Brazzaville n'afọ 2015.
O weputara nke itoolu na afọ 2016 na African Championships in Athletics na Durban na mita 45.40.
N'afọ 2018 ọ nwetara ihe nrite ọlaọcha na Sekondi-Takoradi GAA(Ghana Athletics Association) Circuit na mita 45.35.

N'afọ 2002, Nartey setịpụrụ ihe ndekọ ịgba bọọlụ nke mita 11.70 mgbe ọ nọ na Osei Kyeretwie Senior High School n'oge asọmpi Ashanti Regional Super Zonal athletics nke were afọ 18 ruo mgbe Rashida Abass nke Prempeh College mebiri ya na afọ 2019.
